net.sourceforge.jtds.jdbc

Class SQLParser.ConInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.jtds.jdbc.SQLParser.ConInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    SQLParser

    private static class SQLParser.ConInfo
extends java.lang.Object

    Primitive data structure holding all connection specifics required by the SQL parser.

    Instances of this class may are used as key values in the SQL parser's internal statement cache.

    Author:
    Brett Wooldridge, Alin Sinpalean, Holger Rehn
